                "the",
                "center",
                "sits",
                "the",
                "nucleus",
                "the",
                "cell's",
                "control",
                "room"
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "It stores the cell's DNA, the instructions that tell the cell how to grow, when to divide, and what jobs to perform.",
              "wordList": [
