                "stores",
                "the",
                "cell's",
                "DNA",
                "the",
                "instructions",
                "that",
                "tell",
                "the",
                "cell",
                "how",
                "to",
                "grow",
                "when",
                "to",
                "divide",
                "and",
                "what",
                "jobs",
                "to",
                "perform"
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "Without these instructions, no cell could function.",
