                "the",
                "nucleus",
                "are",
                "tiny",
                "structures",
                "called",
                "organelles",
                "each",
                "with",
                "its",
                "own",
                "special",
                "role"
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "The mitochondria turn food into energy that the rest of the cell can use.",
              "wordList": [
                "The",
                "mitochondria",
                "turn",
                "food",
                "into",
                "energy",
                "that",
                "the",
                "rest",
                "of",
                "the",
                "cell",
                "can",
                "use"
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "The ribosomes build proteins that help the body grow and repair itself.",
              "wordList": [
                "The",
                "ribosomes",
                "build",
                "proteins",
                "that",
                "help",
                "the",
                "body",
                "grow",
                "and",
                "repair",
                "itself"
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "A jelly-like fluid called cytoplasm fills the space between all these busy parts.",
